      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent analyst review of boundary conditions, load application, and material assignments completed; discrepancies resolved and documented.",
      "rationale": "A second analyst independently reconstructed boundary conditions and material assignments from engineering drawings. Two minor discrepancies identified (friction coefficient assignment and load application point offset) were corrected prior to final runs. Peer review documented."
