      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Testing performed at minimum two load levels or two fixture configurations to characterize response across the intended use envelope.",
      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single compression-bending load configuration per ASTM F1717. Only one test condition was applied; the required level of 2 (multiple conditions) was not achieved. This is a documented gap acknowledged by the submitter."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
