      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA input parameters (geometry, material, BCs) traceable to as-tested specimen measurements; any deviations documented and bounded.",
      "rationale": "Specimen-specific geometry and measured material properties used as FEA inputs where available. Friction coefficient treated as nominal with ±20% bounds. All parameter-to-specimen mappings documented in the V&V plan traceability matrix."
    },
