      "rationale": "Three primary QoIs evaluated: construct stiffness (E/uval=1.31), yield force (E/uval=1.54), and force at 40 mm displacement (E/uval=1.78). All below 1.96 threshold. Percent differences 4.8%, 6.2%, and 7.1% respectively, all below 10% bound."
    },
